import React from 'react'

export const SingUpForm = () => {
  return (
    <form>
            <ButtonSignUp
              style={{transform: buttonState ? "scale(.6)" : " scale(1)" }}
            >
              Sign Up
            </ButtonSignUp>
            <Input 
              type='text'
              placeholder="User name"
            />
            <Input 
              type='text'
              placeholder="Email"
            />
            <Input 
              type='text'
              placeholder="Password"
            />
            <Button>Sign Up</Button>
    </form>
  )
}
